description: Tiny mushrooms show as a lighter splotch against the darkened roots of the trees.  The smell of decaying leaves and moist earth wafts in on a vagrant breeze slinking out from the depths of the wooded shadows surrounding the path.

Pale blades of grass struggle to find light beneath the leafy canopy spreading over the path.  The smell of decaying leaves and moist earth wafts in on a vagrant breeze slinking out from the depths of the wooded shadows surrounding the path.
title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, East Woods]
